"| Karkaṭa | śrabaṇā | Juli-aug | Varṣā (moesson) |\n"
"| Siṃha | Bhādra | Aug-sept | Śarad (herfst) |\n"
"| Kanyā | Aśvin | Sept-okt | Śarad (herfst) |\n"
"| Tulā | Kārtik | Okt-nov | Hemanta (Pre-Winter) |\n"
"| Vṛścika | Agāhāna | Nov-dec | Hemanta (Pre-Winter) |\n"
"| Dhanu | Pauṣa | Dec-jan | Śiśira (winter) |\n"
"| Makara | Magha | Jan-feb | Śiśira (winter) |\n"
